parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag Failure and Inadequate Recall Response
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident. The lack of available parts and inadequate response to recall notices can leave vehicles unrepaired, putting drivers and passengers at risk.
symptoms: inability to repair due to unavailable parts
lack of response from manufacturer or dealerships.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of support and communication from dealerships can lead to frustration and delay in addressing safety issues, putting drivers and passengers at risk.

The failure of vehicle safety systems, such as airbags, can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident. Other performance issues can affect the overall safety and reliability of the vehicle.
The failure to repair recalled airbag parts can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Difficulty scheduling an appointment for repair
and lack of communication from the manufacturer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The failure of the brake system can cause accidents or loss of control, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Brake pedal travels to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: clutch pedal feels soft or spongy

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Axle Housing Failure and Rust Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front axle housing can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially lead to serious injuries or fatalities. Rust issues can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, leading to further failures and safety risks.
symptoms: The front end becomes extremely loose
the front axle housing breaks away from its mounting bolts
and other parts underneath the truck
vibrations when applying brakes on downhill slopes or at high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Issues and Front End Problems
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities. Front end problems can lead to loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: vehicle sways and drifts around corners
front end vibration when applying brakes
and other parts underneath the truck.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Wheel bearing failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Medium to extreme front end vibration when applying brakes on downhill slopes or at high speeds
and other parts underneath the truck.
